  <div class="content">
    <div class="about">
      <div class="selfinto">
        <h1 class="title" id="about">Personal Statement</h1>
        <p>
          Experienced in software and networking, I am also passionate about
          accepting various challenges by finishing DofE Gold and solving
          problems by founding a student company. Besides, I was the president
          of the STEM and coding club. Organising and leading some student-led
          robot projects has boosted my confidence in teamwork as well as public
          speaking. I also had numerous experiences volunteering inside and
          outside the school across different age groups, from primary school to
          the elderly. I am motivated and will keep enhancing myself to fit
          better in my position and make a valid contribution.
        </p>
      </div>
